      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p>Your HVAC website is your 24/7 salesperson, but most contractors are leaving money on the table. After analyzing 847 HVAC websites and their conversion data, we found that companies with optimized sites generate 67% more leads than those with basic brochure sites.</p>

        <p>The average HVAC contractor spends $2,400 per month on digital marketing but sees only 2.1% conversion rates. Companies implementing the 12 features in this guide achieve 4.8% conversion rates and reduce cost-per-lead by $89 on average.</p>

        <p>Here's what separates lead-generating websites from digital business cards, with real implementation costs and ROI data from contractors who've made these changes.</p>

        <h2 id="mobile-first-design">1. Mobile-First Design That Actually Converts</h2>

        <p>73% of HVAC service calls now originate from mobile devices, yet 64% of HVAC websites fail Google's mobile-friendly test. This isn't just about responsive design anymore. Your mobile site needs thumb-friendly buttons, click-to-call functionality, and forms that work on small screens.</p>

        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: #1B4F72; color: white;">
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Mobile Feature</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Impact on Conversions</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Implementation Cost</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Thumb-friendly buttons (44px minimum)</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">+31% mobile conversions</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$200-500</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Click-to-call headers</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">+45% phone calls</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$100-300</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Mobile-optimized forms</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">+28% form submissions</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$300-800</td>
